        <abstract> 
<p>Accepts offer of stereotype plates from Murray for <hi rend="italic">Climbing plants</hi>, and will give same terms.</p>  
<p>Has only just made <hi rend="italic">Insectivorous plants</hi> ready. Long and favourable review just appeared in <hi rend="italic">Times</hi>.</p>  
<p>Wants to publish <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi> and so will approach Judd &amp; Co. [publishers of first U. S. edition (1868)].</p> 
        </abstract>
